<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome, <%= name %>!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We are excited to welcome you to our community. Here is some important information for you:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Username: <%= name %>
                </li>
                <li>Subscription Status: Active</li>
                <li>Member Since: September 2024</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>